    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "a quiet, unscripted ending... that sounds so peaceful compared to this constant, buzzing static of just existing. it's like i'm mourning someone who hasn't even died yet, but the person i was is already gone. what do you mean by a \"quiet release\"?",
